AffiniPy integrates several open-source tools, including:
- RDKit (BSD license)
- MDAnalysis (GPL-compatible)
- Meeko and AutoDock Vina (Apache 2.0)
- Dimorphite-DL (MIT license)
- sascorer (MIT license)
- pdb2pqr and Open Babel (varied OSI-approved licenses)
